rutal swath of its gigantic fist of doom.  The mist of blood is almost tangible.  Then the Healer screams at you for distracting him, you all release, and that stupid guy who thought it'd be smart to make Valkyn Warrior loses a bubble and half of xp.  And of course he was just .005 from 50...So you end up logging because of all the insults heading your way.<br>
<br>
Anywho...if anyone actually reads my posts(heh...people reading my posts...funny), just take my word for it and make your stats acceptable without Savagery and Shaman buffs.  Thanks.<br>
<br>
